#

Grilled Chicken Salad with Avocado and Mango

35 min
$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

none

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-proteinlow-carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

saladgrilledhealthyeasy

Description

A refreshing salad featuring grilled chicken, creamy avocado, and sweet mango, topped with a zesty lime dressing.

Ingredients

  • boneless, skinless chicken breasts: 2
  • mixed salad greens: 4 cups
  • ripe avocado: 1
  • ripe mango: 1
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumbers: 1
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cilantro: 1/4 cup (optional)
